5. PRIVACY
   The Software runs locally. It does not transmit Your code or conversation
   data to Licensor. By default the only network calls are License Key
   validation and verified binary download. Two optional features reach the
   network only when You explicitly enable them: importing a chat "share" link
   You paste, and routing context through a cloud LLM provider You configure with
   Your own API key. See SECURITY.md.

